of Representatives, et al., PETITIONERS23–726v.United StatesIdaho, PETITIONER23–727v.UNITED STATESon writs of certiorari to the united states
court of appeals for the ninth circuit[June 26, 2024]Per Curiam.The writs of certiorari before judgment are
dismissed as improvidently granted, and the stays entered by the
Court on January 5, 2024, are vacated.It is so ordered.
